assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: PT Famon Awal Bros Sedaya Tbk operates a network of hospitals in Indonesia. The company primary healthcare services, including cardiovascular and blood vessel services; mother and child services, such as women's health and fitness, pregnancy, baby massage, lactation, child development, and other services; trauma services; and mammography, ultrasonography mammae, pap smear, vaccines, bronchoscopy, endoscopy, and tumor surgery services. It also offers ambulance service for emergency, inter-hospital transfer, home to hospital transfer, patient return, ambulance escort, and disaster response; maternity, child care, and special treatment rooms; medical checkups comprising updated health history, vital sign checks, visual exam, laboratory tests, and screening tests; intensive, neonatal intensive, and pediatric intensive care units; intensive coronary care units; physiotherapy; laboratory tests, which include hematology, blood biochemistry, hormone/endocrine, immunology and viruses, blood clotting factors, anatomic pathology, microbiology, etc.; intermediate and high care units; surgery rooms; and online consultation services. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Kemayoran, Indonesia. PT Famon Awal Bros Sedaya Tbk is a subsidiary of PT Famon Obor Maju.
